The last result resolves an old problem in\nthe theory of functional equations and inequalities posed by Baron and Ger in\n1983.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Jun 2017 18:51:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jun 2017 21:25:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Jun 2017 04:51:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 2 Jul 2017 16:56:37 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2017 08:53:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-01"}
